      "text": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">A 45-year-old female has history of slip in bathroom, complaints of pain in right hip, tenderness in Scarpa’s triangle and normal X-ray. Next investigation is:&nbsp;</span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q5372321",
      "question_audio": null,
      "question_video": null,
      "map_id": 391,
